we present a net write-off rate based on principal losses only (i.e., excluding interest and/or fees) to be consistent with industry convention. in addition,
because we consider uncollectible interest and/or fees in our reserves for credit losses, a net write-off rate including principal, interest and/or fees is also presented. the twelve months ended december31, 2015 reflect the impact of a change
in the timing of charge-offs for card member receivables and loans in certain modification programs from 180 days past due to 120 days past due.
